6. **Aligning GFN to Page Size:**
   ```c
   while ((gfn << PAGE_SHIFT) & (page_size - 1))
       page_size >>= 1;
   ```
   This aligns the GFN to the page size by reducing the page size until the GFN is properly aligned.

7. **Aligning HVA to Page Size:**
   ```c
